name: We're gonna get thru this, with style and grace.
description:
Been thinking about conflict, dynamics, the way the world and relationships are complicated, but, also so much beauty in the layers of nuance and complexity-- and fashion, keeping your style, owning the things that bring you power. And time and temporality-- we keep moving towards our end and through conflict with style and grace. <3

Created using code and the panasonic MX30 with internal mixer feedback.
